The paper discusses reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The use of value function estimation and exploration-exploitation trade-off suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also proposes a new algorithm for deep Q-network, which falls under the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of planning and learning suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper discusses the convergence property of the proposed method, which is a common topic in the sub-category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the use of neural networks in the proposed algorithm suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
